OL,7,FSean Jefferson, 35, from Walsall and
OL,8,FAmy Clarke, 34 from Lichfield are
OL,9,Faccused of subjecting to their
OL,10,Fdaughter to physical abuse before she
OL,11,Fdied in hospital in March 2022.
OL,13,FThe trial is taking place at Stafford
OL,14,FCrown Court.
