OL,7,FThe court heard Clarke was living at a
OL,8,F"tidy and well-presented" address in
OL,9,FHudson Drive, Burntwood,
OL,10,FStaffordshire, where she gave the
OL,11,Fimpression of being a mother who was
OL,12,Fin control while hiding the fact she
OL,13,F"drank a lot of alcohol and she took
OL,14,Fcocaine".
OL,16,FDarcy Leigh's parents deny that they
OL,17,Fare responsible for the injuries,
OL,18,Fwhich includes 47 rib fractures.
