OL,7,FThe court also heard that Darcy's
OL,8,Ffather Sean Jefferson became
OL,9,Fhysterical after being told about his
OL,10,Fdaughter's death and said "sorry"
OL,11,Fmultiple times.
OL,13,F"Volatile relationship that was
OL,14,Fverbally abusive on both sides"
OL,16,FThe jury were read out messages which
OL,17,Fwere retrieved from the pairs' phones
OL,18,F- and showed a volatile relationship
OL,19,Fthat was verbally abusive on both
OL,20,Fsides.
