OL,7,FIn early March 2022 a message from Amy
OL,8,Fto Sean mentioned that he'd threatened
OL,9,Fto "beat her up" while she had her
OL,10,Fdaughter in her arms - referring there
OL,11,Fto Darcy-Leigh, who at this point was
OL,12,Fjust a few weeks old.
OL,14,FLater that March - early in the
OL,15,Fmorning on the 27th - a 999 call was
OL,16,Fmade by Sean. Within 8 minutes
OL,17,Fparamedics arrived to find Darcy-Leigh
OL,18,Fhad been without a heartbeat for some
OL,19,Ftime.
