OL,7,FSean had said "literally she was fine,
OL,8,Fand she was coughing... she's
OL,9,Fliterally stopped breathing on the
OL,10,Fspot".
OL,12,FDarcy-Leigh was seen by professionals
OL,13,Fmany times, the court heard, but they
OL,14,Fmay have been unaware that she should
OL,15,Fhave been registered on a child
OL,16,Fprotection information sharing system.
OL,18,FThe trial was told Darcy-Leigh, who
OL,19,Fwas subject to social services'
OL,20,Finvolvement, was not registered on the
OL,21,Fsystem due to an error.
