OL,7,FThe prosecutor Harpreet Sandhu KC
OL,8,Fadded: "The only adults who had been
OL,9,Fin the house when Darcy-Leigh
OL,10,Fsustained the injuries that led to her
OL,11,Fnot breathing and not having a pulse
OL,12,Fwere Jefferson and Clarke."
OL,14,FJefferson travelled with his daughter
OL,15,Fby ambulance to New Cross Hospital in
OL,16,FWolverhampton.
OL,18,FMr Sandhu said: "There was no doubt
OL,19,Fthat he was seen to be extremely
OL,20,Fupset."
