OL,7,FThe court heard how Darcy-Leigh was
OL,8,Frushed to hospital. Scans showed she
OL,9,Fhad a massive bleed on her brain and
OL,10,Ffractures to both of her legs which
OL,11,Fmay have been as a result of "pulling
OL,12,For twisting" or when her body was
OL,13,Fshaken.
OL,15,FIt's argued some of her rib fractures
OL,16,Fhad been caused days before, others
OL,17,Fweeks before - all, it's argued, from
OL,18,Fchest compression.
