OL,7,FAt hospital, Jefferson told officers
OL,8,Fthat his daughter had woken up at 7am
OL,9,Fand so he took her downstairs.
OL,11,FHe put Darcy-Leigh, who was crying, in
OL,12,Fa baby bouncer in the living room and
OL,13,Fwent to prepare her milk.
OL,15,FMr Sandhu said: "He said that Darcy
OL,16,Fhad been suffering from a cold.
OL,18,F"She sneezed and, as snot came out of
OL,19,Fher nose, she gasped and stopped
OL,20,Fbreathing before she became lifeless."
