OL,7,FJurors were previously told that Darcy-
OL,8,FLeigh's brain injury could have been
OL,9,Fcaused by her parents "violently"
OL,10,Fshaking her or her head striking a
OL,11,Fsurface.
OL,13,FShe was taken to hospital on March 27
OL,14,Fbut died two days later on March 29.
OL,16,FOn Monday, the court heard how
OL,17,FJefferson dialled 999 just before
OL,18,F7.20am on March 27.
