OL,7,FMr Sandhu told jurors that the
OL,8,Finvestigation into the baby's death
OL,9,Fhad taken some time as it was
OL,10,F"complex" with involvement from
OL,11,F"several medical experts".
OL,13,FHe added: "The experts found that
OL,14,FDarcy did not have any medical
OL,15,Fconditions which would explain her
OL,16,Fdeath.
OL,18,F"She died because a traumatic head
OL,19,Finjury had been inflicted upon her.
