OL,7,F"Darcy's head injury was explained by
OL,8,Fan episode of deliberate and forceful
OL,9,Fshaking by another person or persons
OL,10,Fwhich resulted in her head moving back
OL,11,Fand forth".
OL,13,FBoth parents had been with their
OL,14,Fdaughter at Clarke's then-home in
OL,15,FHudson Drive in Burntwood that
OL,16,Fmorning, jurors heard.
OL,18,FIt's said that Sean was hysterical at
OL,19,Fthe news, saying "sorry", and he
OL,20,Fapparently repeated this several
